name: Creation of the insurance record with provider 'Credit Andorra Life' and validation it in Salesforce

steps.name: Setting person's data for creation the record
Check that the page with the text Fecha de nacimiento is opened
Filling the field birth-date with data 11/10/1967
Filling the field zip-code with data 28012
Filling the field email with data hertha.marquardt@yahoo.com
Filling the field phone with data 921602573
Check that the Page with options for insurance services is opened
Click on [I'm Interested] button with the index 5
Check that grateful Modal is displayed
Click on [Close] button on Grateful modal
Check that the Page with options for insurance services is opened
Closing window acierto to avoid displaying pop up 'Leave the page'
Check sorting of the column titled Número del caso with order DESC
Check that Details page was opened

labels.name: suite
labels.value: Validate the standard test case creation
